, its 2024-2025 AI additions are practical: smart email drafting, lead stage prediction, and automated text responses. What makes Follow Up Boss stand out is its integration ecosystem — it connects to 250+ tools, making it the connective tissue of a real estate tech stack. Acquired by Zillow in 2023 but operating independently."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-green-400","children":"Pros"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-1.5","children":[["$","li","Best integration ecosystem in real estate CRM",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Best integration ecosystem in real estate CRM"]}],["$","li","Reliable and fast — trusted by 50,000+ real estate professionals",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Reliable and fast — trusted by 50,000+ real estate professionals"]}],["$","li","Clean UI that agents actually use (adoption is a real issue with CRMs)",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1