tify agents when a lead's search activity suggests they're moving toward a decision — increased frequency of searches, revisiting specific properties, changes in search criteria. The tool complements any CRM well and is often used alongside Follow Up Boss."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-green-400","children":"Pros"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-1.5","children":[["$","li","Behavior-triggered emails dramatically outperform generic sequences",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Behavior-triggered emails dramatically outperform generic sequences"]}],["$","li","Property-specific personalization feels natural, not automated",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Property-specific personalization feels natural, not automated"]}],["$","li","Hot lead alerts catch the decision moment",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipR